[assistant]   - Uses `SSLEnabled` as the Tomcat property name so it maps to `isSSLEnabled()`.
[assistant] - `DataSourceLinkFactoryTest`
[assistant]   - Binds the test datasource under a simple global name to avoid missing intermediate JNDI subcontexts.
[assistant] - `WebappClassLoaderBaseTest`
[assistant]   - Configures resources and starts/stops the webapp class loader before use.
[assistant] 
